888227433970c0f31c3c","tid":1142273,"uid":186375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T21:24:31.000Z","msg":"以前細個記得冇咁難飲<br />\n仲係甜甜地<br />\n細個唔識野有時會偷飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾阿媽發現收埋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能多左投訴依家d 藥水變得好難飲<br />\n俾親&quot;馬尿&quot;我都情願唔飲放係雪櫃俾家人病果陣佢地飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf90d6d046c5ec17d621822e79cbe2d2b259e204","tid":1142273,"uid":9390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"我細個係連聞到藥水陣味都會嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩宜家大左好左d"},{"pid":"12b33ded3c038ef7407effd93eb8130b94c78498","tid":1142273,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:45:47.000Z","msg":"通常叫醫生唔好開藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fde71006a003312b1838c893db083c462957bf9","tid":1142273,"uid":245064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:47:21.000Z","msg":"你叫我食十粒藥都得<br />\n垃圾藥水就真係唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4588d098bec625d584cfbc9d6385e11c0633f2","tid":1142273,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cbecd8b0e0edfb133db8972eb8f2e9cdb8987f6","tid":1142273,"uid":15306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:29:03.000Z","msg":"馬尿真係好難飲<br />\n入口少少甜 之後好咸 <br />\n浸味超怪 諗起都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好work係真"},{"pid":"43ea560691f16736e3613e451a9c441ac946a832","tid":1142273,"uid":217899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:36:50.000Z","msg":"因為人係犯賤既動物，苦你先覺得有益，貴你先覺得值。"},{"pid":"83053e9361153e2e5698c5efe923066e8810311e","tid":11422